    org.hibernate.boot
    This package contains the contracts that make up the Hibernate native bootstrapping API (building a SessionFactory).

    Represents a proposed new approach to allowing hooks into the process of determining the name of database objects (tables, columns, constraints, etc).
    org.hibernate.boot.model.relational  
    org.hibernate.boot.spi

    This package abstracts the SQL dialect of the underlying database.

    Support for Dialect-specific unique constraint definition

    This package defines the "legacy" Hibernate configuration-time metamodel.

    Support for SqmMutationStrategy implementations that use CTE (SQL's Common Table Expression) approach to perform the update/delete

    Support for SqmMutationStrategy implementations that are backed by an "id table" used to temporarily store the ids of entities matching the update/delete restrictions.
